content: I created a profile in forge (and it appears to be valid in forge). However when I upload to simplifier.net it does not render properly - the table view is missing most of the properties, although the details view seems ok. Here is the link: https://www.simplifier.net/Test230/DataSet/

Hi @Chris Munro Sounds like you've uploaded a diffeential profile. Simplifier is not yet capable of expanding the snapshot, so you have to make sure that you upload a profile that contains the full snapshot. We'll add this capability to the platform soon. For now, I suggest you enable the snapshot option in Forge (options menu) and re-upload.
Thanks @Michel Rutten I have tried that and I still get the 'object not rendered' message. However more properties are visible in the 'table' view than before.
Hi @Chris Munro I suggest you use the feedback button on Simplifier to report the issue to the team. Please include a reference to the published profile. We'll try to figure it out.
